Step 1: Create directories
cd ~
mkdir cricket
cd cricket
mkdir ind pak eng aus

Step 2: Create player files
For India:
cd ind
nano cricket_ind

Add 12 player names, one per line, 
Virat Kohli
Rohit Sharma
KL Rahul
Jasprit Bumrah
Ravindra Jadeja
Shreyas Iyer
Hardik Pandya
Shubman Gill
Mohammed Shami
Rishabh Pant
Yuzvendra Chahal
Ravichandran Ashwin

Save (Ctrl+O) and exit (Ctrl+X)

Pakistan
cd ../pak
nano cricket_pak

Add 12 players:
Babar Azam
