Step 3: Merge all files into one list
cd ~/cricket
cat ind/cricket_ind pak/cricket_pak eng/cricket_eng aus/cricket_aus > all_players.txt

Step 4: Sort alphabetically A â†’ Z
sort all_players.txt > all_players_sorted.txt
Check:
cat all_players_sorted.txt
